  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 2cbaeec8dbe84e069925173ac3a6210b, type: 3}
  m_Name: Dlg_Forest_Guardian_Completed
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::ElementalAlchemist.Dialogue.DialogueData
  _speaker: Forest Guardian
  _lines:
  - The grey ghost that climbs from a dying fire. You read the riddle truly.
  - Take the Fragment of Breath. With it, doors that were shut to your hands will open.
  - One word before you go. Strength like this is a road, and a road can be walked the wrong way. Do not lose yourself upon it.
